Package project.star_wars_universe.data

Class AppData

java.lang.Object
project.star_wars_universe.data.AppData
public class AppData extends Object
Represents a collection of all entities of the application. It serves as an intermediate object representing the application data when data from an outside resource should be parsed and loaded into the application or when the data from the application should be serialized and written to an outside resource.
